<span class="header1">Public Service paired with Science/Mathematics (GH)</span>

<p>If your scored high in the "G" and "H" categories, you understand that there are always ways to improve a situation. You have the ability to investigate, explore, and apply information. This will make you a valuable employee.  People like you have discovered important information that has made the world a better place.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree.  It is helpful to have a Master's Degree or Ph.D. if you hope to work in some of these occupations.</p>

